      "message": "Done in PS19: replaced the note+restore+reconnect call sequence with app.onBackgroundPushReceived(isCallPush, triggerReconnect) which serializes the whole sequence on the main thread — timestamps set, restore queued, reconnect requested, then the deactivation timer armed last. The runnable can therefore never fire with the restore still unqueued; once queued, FIFO ordering on the daemon executor guarantees restore-before-deactivate.",
